019-04-27T19:28:59.000Z","msg":"其實係講乜"},{"pid":"13e09d08616fc03a4ae0899ae80a82c5ce225920","tid":1128352,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T19:30:09.000Z","msg":"──經典兩分鐘<br />\n<br />\n呢套戲嘅62分鐘15秒到64分鐘6秒，我會記住呢兩分鐘。從現在開始我浪費咗兩分鐘，呢個係事實，任何人都改變唔到，因為已經過去了。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩分鐘，講述張靜初喺西湖走嚟走去，120秒內一句對白都冇！！只有一堆whatsapp，畫面不斷過場再過場，張靜初由寺內去咗湖邊再去飲茶，戇鳩鳩去咗五六個景一啲作用都冇！<br />\n<br />\n呢幕林志玲扮尼姑，來回睇咗三百次，仍然唔明林志玲扮尼姑係做乜鳩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40ffa4f9b29f31da771e379bba991479e9cf7e0","tid":1128352,"uid":67489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T19:30:09.000Z","msg":"次次播都有追<br />\n<br />\n好睇!"},{"pid":"91caec3e3c28a9f04300f30f8cff1b6c64755875","tid":1128352,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d8228f8aae41e60083565f8034e065326208659","tid":1128352,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T19:28:59.000Z","msg":"其實係講乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T19:31:14.000Z","msg":"講一班戇鳩佬爭一幅叫富春山居圖既畫<br />\n但爭既過程敘事上完全係199999999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a92bb37b62b9f57fdabd27ddd7b49d6d03036f","tid":1128352,"uid":7673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T19:31:39.000Z","msg":"次次見到個名都諗起富山火葬場"},{"pid":"0a518c884140abc8528ae2feb2ca1c966f5eb79e","tid":1128352,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T19:32:11.000Z","msg":"又呻吟"},{"pid":"9e5a7a30c3be9dddfa66b791d5872aec252464a9","tid":1128352,"uid":33651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91caec3e3c28a9f04300f30f8cff1b6c64755875","tid":1128352,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d8228f8aae41e60083565f8034e065326208659","tid":1128352,"u